Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:02.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:08.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't always show my everything to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:12.93,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If this moment was for me
